	* w3m-util.el: Bind `w3m-current-process', `w3m-pop-up-frames',
	`w3m-pop-up-windows', `w3m-popup-frame-parameters',
	`w3m-select-buffer-name' and `w3m-use-tab', and fbind
	`select-frame-set-input-focus' when compiling.
