	* w3m-form.el (w3m-form-replace): Call `set-buffer-modified-p'.
	(w3m-form-field-parse): Do nothing when fid is nil.
	(w3m-form-input-radio): Likewise.
	(w3m-form-get-by-name): New function.
	(w3m-form-input-map): Use it.

